{"tid":437343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港青年菲國坐冤獄十五年","createTime":"2017-10-16T02:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T16:06:58.000Z","uid":9783,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5503f1b0d37c1f312a25c3682af89161c5c477","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"得閒無事行過書局，見到呢本書<br />\n見到個封面唔知點解好想睇，一開始仲以為係高登d故<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/101904_5d47524d9d780267fd76959106cc12f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F101904_5d47524d9d780267fd76959106cc12f9.jpg&h=ea8070b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得好唏噓，雖然有佢都要負一半責任，但無啦啦係咁惡劣環境坐左10幾年，咁就一世，希望佢早日可以翻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de011b4c4498ba253a724b0740c3ae346f4326dd","tid":437343,"uid":6326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"要負一半責，係咪即係要負責<br />\n又點樣冤獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解釋下來龍去脈好嗎"},{"pid":"2a35bfe9f1cce7d57376c401bc100afdecc74672","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"每次看到鄧龍威的Facebook專頁，都有種說不出的感覺：他的一字一句，都在異國牢獄的狹小空間，逐字逐句地打出來。為證明自己的清白，他於菲律賓的監獄苦撐了17年；為引起注意、為要平反，他偷偷用手機於網上呼冤，揭監獄秘辛。<br />\n<br />\n在菲國監獄，有錢駛得鬼推磨，因為沒「錢」，鄧龍威未獲回港機會；有幸有不幸，他又因菲國腐敗，在獄中可用手機上網。小小的一部電話，就是他與香港一別十多年，又與我城重新連接的橋樑，也是他呼冤的途徑。憑著一群相信他的港人熱心幫助，這異鄉階下囚著書鳴冤，於今年書展出書《黑獄第5730天》，希望讓自己的經歷有更多人知道，討回公道。"},{"pid":"a66ab11a35807c341c3451744e84b0f1968ee936","tid":437343,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"香港政府都放棄唔幫冇辦法"},{"pid":"a99b9e0b4be18e9015b4b17c4aa8599feb4e4bdb","tid":437343,"uid":21097,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ab2b544e21eac903f9ca595595973882a430a5","tid":437343,"uid":1712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:40:10.000Z","msg":"白偉俊幾仆街都好<br />\n但都係得佢一個咁多年一直跟呢單野"},{"pid":"f8e2f0b866f69a725cc8334e9e9554fec0675b4e","tid":437343,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"冇冇比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4791c0737d1be32f7ca82608ec5205fd412d1649","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要負一半責，係咪即係要負責<br />\n又點樣冤獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解釋下來龍去脈好嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢講嘅野係真  起先佢係香港做調酒師<br />\n後來同女友分手 去左菲律賓同一個當地好友結伴旅遊 後來比人屈藏毒 用左10年先判案 判左40年 一直坐到而家 同案另外有一個港人比左錢就放左，但係佢地一齊比人拉  而佢個好友就係獄中死左<br />\n<br />\n我想講佢要負嘅責任：第一打死都唔應該去菲律賓，第二識左個好友幾個月就信人，佢入獄好大程度關佢當地好友事"},{"pid":"6361206eaca79997016ef6d52c6f9f1c32c8236c","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白偉俊幾仆街都好<br />\n但都係得佢一個咁多年一直跟呢單野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完本書對佢改觀，老實講一個三唔識七，又唔係係香港，佢幫到咁真係仁至義盡，出錢又出力"},{"pid":"4b9c052fd85e28447b000926da2ce442b515e25e","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講八萬 話多唔多 話少唔少 但比完就可以出翻黎一定會比"},{"pid":"4e08952929dce2d6ee55130a1fa2d1b05709a5a0","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%84%A7%E9%BE%8D%E5%A8%81-444750002396747/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A8%2581-444750002396747%2F&d=oakFjxmgHF0hgzt0QCe%2FC5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9175cdd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%84%A7%E9%BE%8D%E5%A8%81-444750002396747/</a>"},{"pid":"81249e04cd732056061112a0718636143bcfb128","tid":437343,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白偉俊幾仆街都好<br />\n但都係得佢一個咁多年一直跟呢單野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55f8bb851f055f7e7fe7a26bcb3c8954638319c","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/105704_702f0eaffb75414112d8fc34275ef532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F105704_702f0eaffb75414112d8fc34275ef532.jpg&h=e92d4bf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7035bdcf138fe79327f815dfa01d42dc255bbbd8","tid":437343,"uid":9783,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"連登仔見到唔關自己事就負評 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己學生錢方面就唔多幫到 希望出下post令更多人關注 <br />\n<br />\n見到佢facebook連其他國家人都會出聲，都會關注，望住身邊香港人連花少少時間去了解件事都唔肯<br />\n<br />\n港獨？收皮啦好無，從各種小事可以睇得出香港人係幾咁唔團結<br />\n<br />\n自己運動員唔撐，自己人受不公平對待唔幫<br />\n<br />\n香港勁抽！we are hong kong！"},{"pid":"1597f92a0804274785a8a7a790061a4ca3e80278","tid":437343,"uid":21097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"其實佢而家喺FB 有冇籌錢? 我諗佢而家只要有錢都走得甩"},{"pid":"69a15b9035bfd6842473aba380cfa8663efe386e","tid":437343,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac35fd748473d73a8675a7251087e0519960abe3","tid":437343,"uid":13883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講八萬 話多唔多 話少唔少 但比完就可以出翻黎一定會比</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397a6c87979cc345fff70b65fb9926d159c08b8f","tid":437343,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講八萬 話多唔多 話少唔少 但比完就可以出翻黎一定會比</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n父母無？"},{"pid":"d60ac7766f332dfd1b1305a050abaee42d6d63b8","tid":437343,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講八萬 話多唔多 話少唔少 但比完就可以出翻黎一定會比</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾年，如果佢係香港月薪一萬，都百幾萬"},{"pid":"8ed8e9f5e481560d27731bbe7f38fd821b594b00","tid":437343,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 呢本書我上個月都喺書局成本睇哂, 好深刻。<br />\n其實當初只要佢俾錢就解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講八萬 話多唔多 話少唔少 但比完就可以出翻黎一定會比</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾年，如果佢係香港月薪一萬，都百幾萬</blockquote><br />\n唔好話8萬, 出得番黎80萬都要比啦<br />\n借大耳窿都要借<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8ac21a69aeac3ec84a320437bf77fd92c1dfb9","tid":437343,"uid":5